genresAdvancedInfo.name: vinahouse
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Vinahouse is a genre of electronic dance music that originated in Vietnam. It is characterized by its upbeat tempo, heavy use of bass, and incorporation of traditional Vietnamese instruments and melodies. Vinahouse has gained popularity in recent years, particularly among young people in Vietnam and other Southeast Asian countries.
